metadata.name: Nothing No. 1 of 10 - Limited Edition
metadata.description:
Nothing No. 1 - the first Nothing ever!

This is the first Nothing Token we ever created. Unique in Space. 

Nothing Limited Edition is a collector's set of 10 Tokens created by bucksfornothing.com. 

The collection is strictly limited to 10 pieces, with No. 1 representing the first Nothing ever created!

Even that the Token represents actually nothing, we added a small .jpg file for you to present the Item in your gallery to the public.

Don't forget - a part of our profit goes to people who have actually nothing.
